-- Buffett ‘On the Prowl’ for Large Takeovers, He Says in Shareholder Letter
-- B y   E d i t h   M o y
-- 2012-02-25T13:19:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-25/buffett-says-he-s-on-the-prowl-for-large-acquisitions-to-build-berkshire.html
Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A)  Chairman and
Chief Executive Officer  Warren Buffett  says he’s “on the
prowl” for large acquisitions, according to comments made in
his annual letter to shareholders.  “Over time, the businesses we currently own should
increase their aggregate earnings, and we hope also to purchase
some large operations that will give us a further boost,”
Buffett says in the letter.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Edith Moy at 
 echan10@bloomberg.net  